[{"id":715476,"node":"职场话题","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/career","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/4ea0/6fbc/770_mini.png?m=1598935641","description":"前两天对面部门来了个哥们儿，主要是来救火老项目，号称 6 年 java 。HTML 和 CSS 看不懂就算了，毕竟很多老项目后端不太写页面。ajax 看不懂就太离谱了吧，回调取值也不会处理，强烈怀疑是包装出来的 6 年","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715476","replies":165,"created_ts":1602813125,"created":"09:52:05","title":"六年 Java 一句 JS 代码都不会写，正常吗？","author":"LabJo","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/LabJo","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/dc069d26fd71f1aa733e989ecc4ec301?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":715462,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>最近老婆想预定个旅拍，旅拍太火了……</p>\n<p>现在想去的目的地是三亚，比较适合冬季去。但是在选择旅拍机构上我犯了愁，没有什么经验；</p>\n<p>前来论坛问问各位朋友是否有了解的，可以略微说上一二？</p>\n<p>目的地是：三亚</p>\n<p>我们了解到，基本上是三部分构成：机票 + 摄影机构费用 + （自己旅游的费用，部分机构不提供住宿）</p>\n<p>这样，想问问看，最近广告很火的，铂爵、匠古、唯一啥的，哪些公司会比较靠谱？</p>\n<p>另外就是，我爱人看上一个微博上的 TangVision - 邓小棠，他们报价 1 天三亚的是 24800 （中级套餐）</p>\n<p>有人知道这家公司吗？像是很小众的定制化品牌</p>\n<p>望有了解的老哥分享经验，小弟在此谢过了。</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715462","replies":96,"created_ts":1602811962,"created":"09:32:42","title":"想向各位朋友咨询下旅行拍照（婚照）的相关建议","author":"xbigfat","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/xbigfat","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3ac6/9fc3/317571_mini.png?m=1550716873"},{"id":715524,"node":"Python","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/python","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/8613/985e/90_mini.png?m=1598935628","description":"<p>我在做一个闹钟，等到谋个时间就开始执行谋个动作（在下面的案例里面简化为 <code>print('ok')</code>）。请问这是否是最佳办法？因为我担心会不会导致占用内存过高等问题。我看有一个叫 <a href=\"https://pypi.org/project/alarm/\" rel=\"nofollow\">alarm</a> 的库，也是用 while 循环等待时间。以下是我的示例代码：</p>\n<p>在 2020 年 10 月 17 日 10 点 50 分 50 秒的时候触发事件 <code>print('ok')</code></p>\n<pre><code>from datetime import datetime\n\ndef alarm():\n\twhile True:\n\t\tnow = datetime.now().strftime(\"%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S\")\n\t\tif now == '2020-10-17 10:50:50':\n\t\t\tprint('ok')\n\t\t\tbreak\n\n\nif __name__ == '__main__':\n\talarm()\n</code></pre>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715524","replies":93,"created_ts":1602817033,"created":"10:57:13","title":"Python 做一个闹钟，用 while 循环等待时间是否是一个好办法","author":"sudoy","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/sudoy","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/4964/914e/412163_mini.png?m=1592369129"},{"id":715469,"node":"Apple","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1590337894","description":"<p>刘海屏，从单摄到双摄，去掉 3.5 耳机孔 ，这些都是 iPhone 先弄后面其他厂商跟进的吗？</p>\n<p>还有别的吗？</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715469","replies":92,"created_ts":1602812641,"created":"09:44:01","title":"这些年 iPhone “引领”了哪些手机“潮流方向”？","author":"libasten","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/libasten","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f6d4baad62e4ee124d392af83650f37d?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":715501,"node":"问与答","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/qna","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1594743680","description":"<p>降速威胁客户升级, 可以直接拿到明面上来说了么\n今天接到移动客服电话, 说要给我升级 5G 88 套餐,  不是问我要不要升级而是直接升级, 太狂妄了.\n然后说相信你最近也感受到了 4G 变卡了, 升级 5G 可以感受更快的网速, 这是不需要脸了啊</p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715501","replies":72,"created_ts":1602815119,"created":"10:25:19","title":"移动现在都这么狂妄了么","author":"liuky","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/liuky","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/23a72fd500ed7fd0c2eb3d24688da47a?s=24&d=retro"},{"id":715639,"node":"iPhone","node_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone","node_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_mini.png?m=1597325053","description":"<p><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/12608751634/1000\"/></p>\n","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/715639","replies":67,"created_ts":1602832138,"created":"15:08:58","title":"iphone12 美版似乎频段完全覆盖国行版频段并且还多了 mmwave，大家有没有打算买美版","author":"deadtomb","author_url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/deadtomb","author_image":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/fe136